{"Sid":0,"Did":18025,"Id":"282338","Title":"羅東孔子廟正福美行製鼓","ImageUrl":"https://dcm.s3.hicloud.net.tw/excel/object/2020-02-24/de812ac9-6ecd-4a35-9c08-4dc121482062/collection/41fcf632-868f-4e22-81ae-f6fcd1e6d411/108-her-cw-1168-201910252347565db2e16a5063c0.jpg / https://dcm.s3.hicloud.net.tw/excel/object/2020-02-24/de812ac9-6ecd-4a35-9c08-4dc121482062/collection/4d43a9a0-1883-49d4-9106-c1252ba96df1/108-her-cw-1168-201910252347565db2e16a5063c1.jpg","IndexCode":"Culture_Object","CustomColumns":{"Description":"\n\n台灣傳統廟宇通常在廟內龍邊設置銅鐘，在虎邊設置布鼓，羅東孔子廟的鼓係由「正福美行」製作。 　　正福美行源自福建漳州龍溪以製鼓為業的蔡氏家族，由蔡福美於清乾隆年間開始，迄今該家族在中國大陸仍持續傳統製鼓工藝，被列為福建製鼓工藝之保存者。在清光緒年間，蔡心匏渡海來台在新莊開設製鼓舖，並將製鼓工藝傳承給其子蔡寬諒，蔡寬諒即以「正福美行」開業，後遷至三重。蔡心匏亦傳藝予王阿塗，即响仁和之創始人。 　　蔡寬諒曾在戰後來到羅東經商，並成立「新興大旅社」，後因故離開羅東，該旅社建築轉賣並改名為「遠東旅社」。除經商外，蔡寬諒仍持續其製鼓本業，羅東、冬山多座廟宇均購置正福美行所製之鼓。\n\n","Keyword_Rights_2":"CC BY / CC BY","Keyword_Des_Rights_2":"CC0","Keyword_Longitude":"121.4915987","Keyword_Latitude":"25.0695148","Original_Url":"https://cmsdb.culture.tw/object/61468CA4-6071-4884-9F69-2B3C619E12C4","Original_Identifier":"282338","Keyword_Subject_1":"民俗與宗教","alias":"","alternativeHeadline":"","Keywords":"王阿塗 / 正福美行 / 鼓 / 蔡心匏 / 蔡寬諒 / 羅東孔子廟 / 响仁和","dates":"創作時間 / 民國/戰後時期","LastUpdateTime":"2020/02/24 19:49:57","Creator":"蔡寬諒","publisher":"","mediaType":"有形文物","language":"","timelines":"","city":"新北市三重區","address":"六張街","lng":"121.4915987","lat":"25.0695148","contributors":"","contributor":"葉永韶/ 蔡明志","size":"","admin":"","award":"","character":"","contentLocation":"","acquireWay":"","acquireSource":"","storage":"","version":"","isbn":"","onlineAuthLink":"","stuff":"","url":"","createOrgName":"宜蘭縣政府文化局","citation":"","Keyword_Rights_1":"","AllImages":"https://dcm.s3.hicloud.net.tw/excel/object/2020-02-24/de812ac9-6ecd-4a35-9c08-4dc121482062/collectionOpen/416d304e-5181-4f8a-85fe-c902cd386937/108-her-cw-1168-re-201910252350195db2e16a5063c0.jpg / https://dcm.s3.hicloud.net.tw/excel/object/2020-02-24/de812ac9-6ecd-4a35-9c08-4dc121482062/collectionOpen/f37ef22a-edb9-